<!DOCTYPE html><html lang="id">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Undangan Diana & Juan</title><style>
body{
    font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
    text-align:center;
    background:#f7f7f7;
    padding:20px;
}

.container{
    background:white;
    max-width:600px;
    margin:auto;
    padding:30px;
    border-radius:20px;
    box-shadow:0 0 12px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
}

h1{
    color:#d63384;
}

#countdown{
    font-size:22px;
    margin-top:15px;
}

button{
    padding:12px 25px;
    border:none;
    border-radius:12px;
    background:#ff6b81;
    color:white;
    font-size:16px;
    cursor:pointer;
}
</style></head><body><div class="container"><h1>Diana & Juan</h1><p>Dengan hormat, kami mengundang Bapak/Ibu/Saudara/i<br>
pada acara pernikahan kami</p><h2>14 Maret 2027</h2><p>📍 Kediaman mempelai wanita<br>
Jl. Jend. Sudirman</p><div id="countdown"></div><br><button onclick="playMusic()">🎵 Putar Musik</button>

<audio id="music" loop>
<source src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/nai99business-ai/Theme/main/A%20Thousand%20Years%202.mp3">
</audio></div><script>
function countdown(){
    const eventDate = new Date("2027-03-14").getTime();

    setInterval(function(){
        let now = new Date().getTime();
        let distance = eventDate - now;

        let days = Math.max(0, Math.floor(distance/(1000*60*60*24)));

        document.getElementById("countdown").innerHTML =
        "⏳ Menuju hari bahagia: " + days + " hari lagi";
    },1000);
}

function playMusic(){
    document.getElementById("music").play();
}

countdown();
</script></body>
</html>
